  section.hero.is-fullheight
    .hero-body
      .container
        h1.title Forge
        h2.subtitle The best engineering teams are built with Forge.
        p Forge is a collection of tools to help engineering managers develop maximally effective teams.
        br
        +callToAction

  section.section.is-medium
    .container
      h1.title Make decisions with data, not your gut
      .columns
        .column
          h2.subtitle Are any of my engineers blocked?
          p.
            Check whether engineers are stuck at a glance. Keep an eye on risky,
            critical, or complex work.
        .column
          h2.subtitle Is any work falling behind?
          p.
            Find work that's been repeatedly delayed. Never be
            surprised by an off-track status update.
        .column
          h2.subtitle Are any PRs stuck?
          p.
            Identify stuck PRs at a glance. See trends in stuck work to identify
            potential bottlenecks.

  section.section.is-medium
    .container
      h1.title Manage transparently
      .columns
        .column
          h2.subtitle Transparent performance metrics
          p.
            Accountability comes from transparency. Keep you and your team
            aligned on how they're doing.
        .column
          h2.subtitle Never lose context
          p.
            Provide structure to standups, check-ins, and meetings. Make sure
            key information is shared to the people who need to know.
        .column
          h2.subtitle Keep a pulse on your team
          p.
            Run quick, recurring check-ins with your team. Understand when and
            where people need help.

  section.section.is-medium
    .container
      h1.title Think more clearly
      .columns
        .column
          h2.subtitle Switch contexts less
          .content
            p.
              Switching, searching, and cross-referencing between tools
              interrupts thinking.
            p.
              Integrate with things you already use:
            ul
              li Jira
              li GitHub
              li Slack
            p.
              Use our API to export data or build your own integrations.
        .column
          h2.subtitle Plan more effectively
          content
            p.
              Do you find Jira to be a delightful user experience?<br />
              <br />
              This product is probably not for you.
        .column
          h2.subtitle Save head space
          p.
            "Who is in the office today?"<br />
            "Did the customer team provide more information about that ticket?"<br />
            "Who's next on rotation?"<br />
            <br />
            Mental energy is scarce. Don't spend it on the small stuff.

